    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. This unit delivers a visceral mechanical experience through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential. The chassis is well-sorted, featuring reinforced rear subframe points and refreshed bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly remains within tolerance. While the finish reflects its status as a driven enthusiast vehicle, the powertrain and suspension geometry remain optimized for high-performance applications.",
